http-response-jq ^https:\/\/api\.cc\.163\.com\/v\d\/mgamerecpage\/recommend_page\? '.data.plugins|=map(select(.module_type!="banner"))|.data.plugins|=map(select(.module_type!="show_list"))|.data.plugins|=map(select(.title!="推荐品类"))'
